snippet: Stanislas Wawrinka showed that his first Grand Slam title wasn't a fluke, upstaging his more illustrious countryman to add a maiden Masters trophy in Monte Carlo on Sunday....

headline.print_headline: Wawrinka Beats Federer to Win Monte Carlo Masters
headline.main: Wawrinka Beats Federer to Win Monte Carlo Masters

lead_paragraph: Stanislas Wawrinka showed that his first Grand Slam title wasn't a fluke, upstaging his more illustrious countryman to add a maiden Masters trophy in Monte Carlo on Sunday.
